tourism company.

40:57.422 --> 40:58.623
For your sake,
I hope you're right.

40:58.623 --> 41:02.293
When you call us next time,
it'll be $250,000 for 10%.

41:02.293 --> 41:03.594
[ Laughter ]

41:03.594 --> 41:05.396
-See you, Mike. Congratulations.
-Thanks.

41:05.396 --> 41:06.631
-Good luck, guys.
-Good luck.

41:06.631 --> 41:08.766
Jornlin: I don't feel
disappointed at all.

41:08.766 --> 41:10.601
Who in our line of work

41:10.601 --> 41:12.603
